Package sailpoint.api.nativeidentitychange

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    NativeIdentityChangePropagator
    Interface of NativeIdentityChangeEvent propagators.
    StringReplacer
    Interface for string replacement.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractNativeIdentityChangePropagator
    Abstract base class that implements NativeIdentityChangePropagator.
    AbstractNativeIdentityChangeRolePropagator
    This class provides an abstract implementation of NativeIdentityChangePropagator that propagates NativeIdentityChangeEvents to all Bundles.
    AccountNativeIdentityChangeIdentityPropagator
    This will propagate account type native identity changes to Identity objects by creating 'Identity Refresh Partition' Request for the Identities.
    GroupNativeIdentityChangeIdentityPropagator
    This will propagate group type native identity change to Identity object by creating 'Identity Refresh Partition' Request for all group members.
    NativeIdentityChangeApplicationPropagator
    This class provides an implementation of NativeIdentityChangePropagator that propagates NativeIdentityChangeEvents to all Applications.
    NativeIdentityChangeCorrelationConfigPropagator
    This class provides an implementation of NativeIdentityChangePropagator that propagates NativeIdentityChangeEvents to all CorrelationConfigs.
    NativeIdentityChangeDynamicScopePropagator
    This class provides an implementation of NativeIdentityChangePropagator that propagates NativeIdentityChangeEvents to all DynamicScopes.
    NativeIdentityChangeFormPropagator
    This class provides an implementation of NativeIdentityChangePropagator that propagates NativeIdentityChangeEvents to all Forms.
    NativeIdentityChangeGenericPropagator
    This class provides an implementation of NativeIdentityChangePropagator that delegates all propagation logic to a rule.
    NativeIdentityChangeGroupDefinitionPropagator
    This class provides an implementation of NativeIdentityChangePropagator that propagates NativeIdentityChangeEvents to all GroupDefinitions.
    NativeIdentityChangeIdentityTriggerPropagator
    This class provides an implementation of NativeIdentityChangePropagator that propagates NativeIdentityChangeEvents to all IdentityTriggers.
    NativeIdentityChangePasswordPolicyHolderPropagator
    This class provides an implementation of NativeIdentityChangePropagator that propagates NativeIdentityChangeEvents to all PasswordPolicyHolders.
    NativeIdentityChangePolicyPropagator
    This class provides an implementation of NativeIdentityChangePropagator that propagates NativeIdentityChangeEvents to all GenericConstraints and ActivityConstraints (which are referenced by Policies.
    NativeIdentityChangeRolePropagatorCorrelationModel
    A role propagator which searches the in-memory CorrelationModel for relevant Bundles rather than querying the database.
    NativeIdentityChangeRulePropagator
    This class provides an implementation of NativeIdentityChangePropagator that propagates NativeIdentityChangeEvents to all Rules.
    NativeIdentityChangeUtil  
    NativeIdentityStringReplacer
    Native Identity String replacement class.

    Exception Description
    UnfinishedNativeIdentityChangeException
